msgid ""
"Zangemann original ice cream machine. It is ice blue in color and is similar "
"to a vending machine of drinks, but instead of the cup there is a cone that "
"is filled with ice cream. Above the dispenser there is a monitor showing the "
"variety that is distributed, in this case pineapple ice cream. On the left "
"there are the slot for inserting coins, the various buttons to choose the "
"flavor, and the hole for returning coins. At the top there is a round white "
"sign with a scoop of candy-pink ice cream in a cone. On the back of the "
"machine there is the refrigeration machinery with the “Z” of the Zangemann "
